title: 아주 멋진 프로젝트 이름
content:
Ross: What? Wh- hello? The Millners' farm in Connecticut? 
The Millners, they had this unbelievable farm, they had horses, and,
 andrabbits that he could chase and it was- it w- .....Oh my God, Chi Chi!
Phoebe: It's not mine, I didn't earn it, if I kept it, it would be
 like stealing. Rachel: Yeah, but if you spent it, it would be like 
 shopping!
